To import users, create an Excel file that meets the following conditions:
The file must be at least a Microsoft Excel 2007 file;
The first row must be the header row;
All values must be valid according to the [productName] validation rules;
Password are optional. If no password is entered, [productName] will create an unique password for the user;
Groups are optional. If no group is entered, the users will be added to the %s group;
Groups must match the exact label available in [productName];
Multiple groups can be specified, seperated by a semicolon (;).
The maximum amount of users which can be imported at once is %s.
